{"tid":720774,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「處境題」搭扶手電梯","createTime":"2018-06-28T07:49:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-28T11:51:10.000Z","uid":173453,"like":26,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"e2e63875e1025ef8898b4c2ac0f7d0a70cc4dc77","tid":720774,"uid":173453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T07:49:10.000Z","msg":"雖然無文明規定電梯係左行右企<br />\n但而家普遍既人都會有呢個概念且實行<br />\n問題黎喇<br />\n假設你要搭一條好長既扶手電梯<br />\n你好撚攰唔想行所以諗住去右手邊<br />\n但點知俾人逼下逼下逼到去左手邊<br />\n右手邊又無位俾你zip番入去<br />\n咁你會點做法？<br />\n<br />\n正評：無計，焗撚住行<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負評：理鳩你繼續企係左手邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"814b6c443d10a620f735e0dce716e2e32202ad9b","tid":720774,"uid":41817,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T07:50:33.000Z","msg":"塞左後面自己都唔好意思啦<br />\n香港人一秒鐘幾百萬上落<br />\n想俾後面屌咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc5cbb258bd048f37e96ab9ee37fc34030820a0","tid":720774,"uid":28831,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"點解會比人迫去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"daeda8566cf52bd3b87ef9a91e01befb58497439","tid":720774,"uid":74262,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T08:00:44.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"734b33fdae73f2e549373f89249ea0ff64331064","tid":720774,"uid":173453,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"7dc5cbb258bd048f37e96ab9ee37fc34030820a0","tid":720774,"uid":28831,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T07:53:27.000Z","msg":"點解會比人迫去左邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-28T10:41:24.000Z","msg":"事緣係頭先搭地鐵見到條友唔排隊想打尖插入去右手邊<br />\n但佢插入果下時機唔夠準<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n加上又無人讓佢<br />\n咁佢就滯留左係左手邊<br />\n但左手邊又有人係佢後面<br />\nSorry 1999<img src=\"/assets/faces/no